// Demo dataset for the Intranet example.
// Employee portraits and article covers are generated gradient SVGs (initials /
// emoji) embedded as base64 documents, same approach as models/b2c-app covers.
// Employees whose `_user_pending_link` matches a seed user email are claimed by
// that user at first login (see docs/Security.md).
// Note: article.author is calculated (copy_logged_on_insert), so seeded articles
// have no author; it is auto-linked when a logged-in employee creates an article.
