    "article": [
      {
        "title": "Welcome to the New Employee Portal",
        "category": "company-news",
        "summary": "Directory with org chart, clock-in from your browser, vacation requests with one click and a helpdesk for HR and IT — all in one place.",
        "body": "# Welcome to the New Employee Portal\n\nThe intranet you are reading this on is also your new **self-service portal**. Everything that used to need an email to HR now takes a couple of clicks.\n\n## What you can do here\n\n* **Find people** — search the directory or browse the org chart, photos included.\n* **Clock in and out** — the time tracking page keeps your flexibility balance up to date.\n* **Request time off** — vacations and short leaves go straight to the HR inbox; you can follow the state of each request.\n* **Open tickets** — one helpdesk for HR *and* IT requests.\n\n## Getting started\n\n1. Sign in with your corporate account.\n2. Check your profile (photo, phone, work center) and ask HR to fix anything that is off.\n3. Bookmark the portal — announcements land here first.\n\n> Feedback is welcome: open an **IT ticket** with the `portal` word in the subject and we will triage it weekly.",
        "published_date": "2026-06-20",
        "status": "published",
        "is_featured": true,
        "documents": [
          { "tag": "img_m", "name": "cover.svg", "content_type": "image/svg+xml", "content_base64": "" }
        ]
      },
      {
        "title": "Summer Intensive Schedule Starts July 1",
        "category": "hr-announcements",
        "summary": "From July 1 to August 31 the working day ends at 15:00. Remember to keep clocking your real hours.",
        "body": "# Summer Intensive Schedule\n\nBetween **July 1 and August 31** we switch to the intensive summer schedule:\n\n| | Regular | Summer |\n| --- | --- | --- |\n| Start | 09:00 | 08:00 |\n| End | 18:00 | 15:00 |\n| Lunch | 1 hour | — |\n\n## What does NOT change\n\n* Clock in and out as usual — the portal computes your flexibility balance automatically.\n* Vacation requests keep needing HR approval **before** you book flights.\n\n## Reminders\n\n1. Coordinate coverage within your team before requesting Fridays off.\n2. The office AC shuts down at 16:00 — another reason to leave on time. ☀️",
        "published_date": "2026-06-25",
        "status": "published",
        "documents": [
          { "tag": "img_m", "name": "cover.svg", "content_type": "image/svg+xml", "content_base64": "" }
        ]
      },
      {
        "title": "New VPN: Migration Guide",
        "category": "it-tools",
        "summary": "The old VPN is retired on July 15. Install the new client and enrol your device in under ten minutes.",
        "body": "# New VPN: Migration Guide\n\nWe are replacing the legacy VPN with a faster, always-on client. The old gateway is **switched off on July 15**.\n\n## How to migrate\n\n1. Install the new client from the software center (`Company VPN 2`).\n2. Sign in with your corporate account — no separate password.\n3. Approve the device enrolment notification on your phone.\n4. Test: open the intranet from outside the office network.\n\n## Troubleshooting\n\n* *Stuck at enrolment?* Reboot once; 90% of cases solved.\n* *Legacy tools failing?* They may pin the old gateway — open an **IT ticket** and we will migrate the config with you.\n\n> Working from abroad in summer? Check the travel policy first, then request the roaming profile through a ticket.",
        "published_date": "2026-06-18",
        "status": "published",
        "documents": [
          { "tag": "img_m", "name": "cover.svg", "content_type": "image/svg+xml", "content_base64": "" }
        ]
      },
      {
        "title": "Q2 All-Hands on July 10",
        "category": "company-news",
        "summary": "Quarter results, the product roadmap for H2 and a live Q&A. Friday July 10 at 12:00 in Madrid HQ and streamed everywhere.",
        "body": "# Q2 All-Hands\n\nJoin us on **Friday, July 10 at 12:00** for the quarterly all-hands.\n\n## Agenda\n\n* **12:00** — Q2 results (Diana)\n* **12:25** — H2 product roadmap (Iván)\n* **12:45** — People updates: new joiners and internal moves (Marta)\n* **12:55** — Open Q&A\n\n## Where\n\n* Madrid HQ — auditorium, 3rd floor\n* Barcelona Office — main meeting room, streamed\n* Remote — link in the calendar invite\n\nQuestions can be submitted in advance through the usual form; anonymous ones welcome.",
        "published_date": "2026-07-01",
        "status": "published",
        "documents": [
          { "tag": "img_m", "name": "cover.svg", "content_type": "image/svg+xml", "content_base64": "" }
        ]
      },
      {
        "title": "Office Refurbishment Plans",
        "category": "company-news",
        "summary": "Draft: floor plans and phased schedule for the Madrid HQ refurbishment.",
